cu.explanation_en: Setting the RRC log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause the logging system to fail initialization for RRC components and may impair system debugging and monitoring capabilities.

du.explanation_en: Setting the number of transmit antennas to zero '0' will cause radio unit configuration failure and prevent proper transmission initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將發射天線數量設定為零 '0' 會導致無線單元配置失敗，並阻止正確的發射初始化。
